{"tid":1374711,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"港女喎","createTime":"2019-07-28T00:02:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T01:28:42.000Z","uid":284779,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"08c02fe7ee4ba7c7ff77932f6f19048716196e7d","tid":1374711,"uid":284779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T00:02:17.000Z","msg":"香港女仔真係娶得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總結呢兩個月都係受&ldquo;港女&rdquo;款待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n612：主動過黎清洗，派食物<br />\n<br />\n615：要比個女仔安慰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n626：比班女仔送上車<br />\n<br />\n629：比個女仔拍背隻安慰<br />\n<br />\n71：我●好●撚●想●喊<br />\n<br />\n714，727：分佢身上d裝備，急救<br />\n<br />\n我地要珍惜身邊既巴絲，我好撚攰。<br />\n唔知仲可以行幾耐，我從心底好感觸自己係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我好愛你地 <br />\n希望有一日我地相識唔需要帶住口罩，裝備，頭盔。<br />\n<br />\n個一日我想知道你地既名同見到你地既樣，我既戰友，我既香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港義士不論男女 都值得拎榮譽勳章。<br />\nWe are Hong Kongers <br />\n<br />\n落緊既日子 可唔可以<br />\n一齊出去 就 一齊返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e1e10abc8ba26c333c706b85b68d861ff8d99e1","tid":1374711,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T01:10:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ec8b8ef1b8f080803b518dbb11bceb964c02a7b","tid":1374711,"uid":59608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T01:10:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/ass